WEBVTT

00:02.480 --> 00:04.134
ISA, me and the wife,
we never really fit in.

00:04.134 --> 00:06.049
<i>Jordan was a good guy,
but the rest of 'em,</i>

00:06.049 --> 00:07.616
<i>I do not miss.</i>

00:07.616 --> 00:09.139
Howdy, neighbor.

00:09.139 --> 00:11.663
We have got to get
together for coffee!

00:11.663 --> 00:14.623
I love Blue Valley
and the people in it.

00:14.623 --> 00:16.233
You stopped Icicle.

00:16.233 --> 00:18.235
[screams] <i>
You got me justice.</i>

00:18.235 --> 00:20.281
That was an accident, pal.

00:20.281 --> 00:23.110
<i>Took off the limiter.
Now it works 24/7.</i>

00:23.110 --> 00:24.285
Rick, stop!

00:30.900 --> 00:32.728
Sofus!
He's having

00:32.728 --> 00:34.338
