What do we do?

00:34.338 --> 00:36.079
I'm still worried
about Cindy.

00:36.079 --> 00:37.254
What's that?

00:37.254 --> 00:38.168
It looks like a list

00:38.168 --> 00:39.952
of her father's laboratories.

00:39.952 --> 00:41.302
<i>Our lead.</i>

00:41.302 --> 00:43.304
If you wanna find Cindy,
let's find Cindy.

00:45.262 --> 00:47.003
Oh, boy.

00:54.489 --> 00:59.102
I'll kill
every last one of them.

01:18.600 --> 01:20.819
<i>♪ If you love somebody</i>

01:20.819 --> 01:22.647
<i>♪ Better tell them
while they're here ♪</i>

01:22.647 --> 01:27.783
<i>♪ 'Cause they just may
run away from you ♪</i>

01:27.783 --> 01:30.307
<i>♪ You'll never know
what, when, where ♪</i>

01:30.307 --> 01:32.309
<i>♪ Then again,
it just depends ♪</i>

01:32.309 --> 01:37.662
<i>♪ On how long of time
is left for you ♪</i>

01:37.662 --> 01:40.839
<i>♪ Now take it in,
but don't look down ♪</i>

01:40.839 --> 01:43.364
<i>all: ♪ 'Cause I'm on top
of the world, hey! ♪</i>

