<i>♪ Take you with me if I can</i>

01:57.552 --> 02:00.381
<i>♪ Been dreaming of this
since a child ♪</i>

02:00.381 --> 02:03.775
<i>♪ I'm on top of the world</i>

02:03.775 --> 02:06.474
<i>♪ I've tried to cut
these corners ♪</i>

