02:36.721 --> 02:39.376
<i>♪ And I know it's hard
when you're falling down ♪</i>

02:39.376 --> 02:41.770
<i>♪ And it's a long way up
when you hit the ground ♪</i>

02:41.770 --> 02:45.556
<i>♪ But get up now,
get up, get up now ♪</i>

02:45.556 --> 02:47.993
<i>♪ 'Cause I'm on top
of the world, hey! ♪</i>

